{"tid":804034,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★[700?]康樂園夫婦疑財困燒炭　男死女命危","createTime":"2018-09-02T17:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T09:35:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5668fc630a4c44d1e253bd35dd4688f945fed82e","tid":804034,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"康樂園夫婦疑財困燒炭，男死女獲救。今晚(2日)8時許，警方接獲一名女子報案，指其弟弟及弟婦，昏迷倒臥在大埔康樂園一間獨立屋內。救護員接報趕至，替2人急救後，再將他們急送往大埔那打素醫院搶救，惜姓陸(64歲)男事主最後不治，姓馬(61歲)女事主經救治後，情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，企圖自殺夫婦為退休商人，與外傭同住，外傭今日放假外出，返回上址發現單位大門貼有字條，寫着「不要內進」，同時聞到有燒炭的氣味，擔心戶主夫婦發生意外，連忙通知男戶主的親友，男戶主家姐到場了解，同時報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方在涉事單位內，發現一盆燒過的炭，同時檢獲遺書，內容提及經濟問題，經初步調查後，相信事件沒有可疑，案件列作企圖自殺，不排除<span style=\"color: red;\">戶主夫婦受經濟問題困擾</span>，而萌輕生念頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180902/bkn-20180902212723558-0902_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180902%2Fbkn-20180902212723558-0902_00822_001.html&d=nxtd%2Bd32wDQI7AuCi7YvBtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=793706c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180902/bkn-20180902212723558-0902_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2af5cca8e4d8846c6fd653f6bfaf294046ee5fd0","tid":804034,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:14:27.000Z","msg":"廢老退晒休都有經濟問題？"},{"pid":"fc0d36a559698107d7c822f2e8596b5487e1cfe3","tid":804034,"uid":136727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"老魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd328d72dae1906c3ad5b274b0ac8146782f6d0","tid":804034,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:27:03.000Z","msg":"諗住allin qq 收下息姐"},{"pid":"c5b27cb5d697e456f8393a0059e216895de0601